'''Ithor''' was a group of three [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] in the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. They arrived to pick up a shipment of warheads stolen from [[Viraxo Industries]] by [[Container transport|Container Transport]] group [[Magnum Group|''Magnum'']] lead by [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen]] in the [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300 light freighter]] ''[[Sabra]]''.

